Statement
\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset


\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "subsec:Statement-lifting-function-relation-covariant-1"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

(a) below will show that 
