 For arbitrary values 
\begin_inset Formula $g_{1}^{:R\rightarrow A}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $g_{2}^{:R\rightarrow B}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $h_{1}^{:A\rightarrow S}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $h_{2}^{:B\rightarrow S}$
\end_inset

