\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Defining the profunctor 
\begin_inset Formula $N^{X,Y}\triangleq\left(R\rightarrow Y\right)\times\left(X\rightarrow S\right)$
\end_inset

, we find that 
\begin_inset Formula $g_{1}\times h_{1}$
\end_inset

 has type 
\begin_inset Formula $N^{A,A}$
\end_inset

