\begin_inset Formula $c\triangleq f(a)$
\end_inset

, and then we obtain the same pullback condition relating 
\begin_inset Formula $a$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $b$
\end_inset

, namely 
\begin_inset Formula $f(a)=g(b)$
\end_inset

.
