, 
\begin_inset Formula $y^{:P^{Y,Y}}$
\end_inset

, and 
\begin_inset Formula $f^{:X\rightarrow Y}$
\end_inset

.
 If 
\begin_inset Formula $(x,y)\in\text{push}\,(f^{\downarrow P},f^{\uparrow P})$
